<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Admin Dashboard</title>
    <link href="/assets/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/assets/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f6f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .sidebar {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 250px;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: #1a1a2e;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .sidebar h4 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #9850E4;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .sidebar a {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }
        .sidebar a i {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .sidebar a:hover {
            background-color: #9850E4;
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }
        .main {
            margin-left: 270px;
            padding: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .main h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .main p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .welcome-box {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            display: inline-block;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .logout-btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #dc3545;
            border: none;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 16px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .logout-btn:hover {
            background-color: white;
            color: #dc3545;
            font-weight: bold;
            border: 1px solid #dc3545;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="sidebar">
        <h4>Admin Panel</h4>
        <a href="/admin"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Dashboard</a>
        <!-- <a href="/collegeDetails"><i class="fas fa-building"></i> College Details</a> -->
        <a href="/discipline"><i class="fas fa-book"></i> Discipline</a>
        <a href="/branches"><i class="fas fa-code-branch"></i> Branches</a>
        <a href="/subjects"><i class="fas fa-book-open"></i> Subjects</a>
        <a href="/faculty"><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i> Faculty</a>
        <a href="/mapping"><i class="fas fa-map"></i> Mapping</a>
        <a href="/server"><i class="fas fa-server"></i> Server</a>
        <a href="/report"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Report</a>
        <a href="/teacher-remarks"><i class="fas fa-comment"></i> Faculty Remarks</a>
        <form action="/logout?_method=DELETE" method="POST" style="display:inline;">
            <button type="submit" class="logout-btn">Logout</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="main">
        <div class="welcome-box">
            <h1>Welcome, Admin!</h1>
            <p>You have full access to manage the Faculty Feedback System. Use the sidebar to navigate through different sections.</p>
            <ul>
                <li><b>Dashboard:</b> Get an overview of the system.</li>
                <li><b>College Details:</b> Manage details related to the college.</li>
                <li><b>Discipline & Branches:</b> Configure disciplines and branches.</li>
                <li><b>Subjects & Faculty:</b> Add and manage subjects and faculty members.</li>
                <li><b>Mapping:</b> Assign subjects to semesters and faculty to subjects.</li>
                <li><b>Server Control:</b> Enable or disable feedback collection.</li>
                <li><b>Reports:</b> View feedback analysis and faculty remarks.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>For any issues, contact the technical support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>